### Put records only if it doesn't exist
POST http://localhost:8190/records/put
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "Records": [
    {
      "pk": "pk1",
      "sk": "sk1",
      "data": {
        "hey": "ho"
      },
      "if": "data == null"
    }
  ]
}

### Delete records if
POST http://localhost:8190/records/delete
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "Records": [
    {
      "pk": "pk1",
      "sk": "sk1",
      "if": "_updated_at > 1"
    }
  ]
}